{"tid":2040279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★港版國安法：港銀行、航運、物流業恐遭徹底摧毀","createTime":"2020-05-28T12:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T13:10:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33af1f4269f07a9bc4f7910555f0528f0d19bb07","tid":2040279,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，Enodo Economics首席經濟學家Diana Choyleva警告：如果美國結束1992年《美國－香港政策法》賦予香港的所有特權，香港經濟將基本消失。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，最重要的是，法律規定港元可以自由兌換美元，若美國採取行動限制香港金融管理局自由兌換美元，那將是個「極端的核選項」，恐摧毀香港銀行業、航運業和物流業，同時引發大範圍的資本外逃。<br />\n她又預期，中國將繼續推動把上海變為國際金融中心，把深圳港變成國際貿易中心，外國企業將不得不在缺乏法治的中國求生存，「這是個大脫鈎的過程，全球經濟未來勢必將分裂成兩個勢力範圍」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200528/bkn-20200528144417006-0528_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200528%2Fbkn-20200528144417006-0528_00842_001.html&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu4lS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=cfee7e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200528/bkn-20200528144417006-0528_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0be69d0d8bc4ae4b4cee637606309b57400c11e0","tid":2040279,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4juvGGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4juvGGW.jpg&h=e0602593&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0002428550e8f9afa906a1f88b92b5f235a405c9","tid":2040279,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"不怕，信政府！"},{"pid":"0a3a22d8d6b32c68d052306a6926420423c91c6d","tid":2040279,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKDMcrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKDMcrH.jpg&h=9c166a3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"606ec9a0ee35ed9c258a1ffb2d94ca369d76ee8b","tid":2040279,"u